### Coupons Script API Tests
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code to use this file
### Click "Send Request" above each request to test

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ============================================
### STORE APIs (5)
### ============================================

### 1. Get All Stores
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores

### 2. Get Store by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/amazon

### 3. Create Store
POST {{baseUrl}}/stores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Amazon",
  "slug": "amazon",
  "logo": "https://logo.clearbit.com/amazon.com",
  "description": "World's largest online retailer",
  "website": "https://amazon.com"
}

### 4. Update Store (replace :id with actual store ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stores/STORE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Amazon Updated",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 5. Delete Store (replace :id with actual store ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/stores/STORE_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### COUPON APIs (7)
### ============================================

### 6. Get All Coupons
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons

### 7. Get Coupon by ID (replace :id with actual coupon ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE

### 8. Get Coupons by Store (replace :storeId with actual store ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons/store/STORE_ID_HERE

### 9. Get Coupons by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons/category/electronics

### 10. Create Coupon (replace store ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "50% Off Electronics",
  "code": "SAVE50",
  "description": "Get 50% off on all electronics",
  "discount": "50% OFF",
  "store": "STORE_ID_HERE",
  "expiryDate": "2024-12-31",
  "isActive": true,
  "isFeatured": true
}

### 11. Update Coupon (replace :id with actual coupon ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "60% Off Electronics - Updated",
  "discount": "60% OFF"
}

### 12. Delete Coupon (replace :id with actual coupon ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### ANALYTICS APIs (2)
### ============================================

### 13. Reveal Coupon Code (replace :couponId with actual coupon ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons/reveal/COUPON_ID_HERE

### 14. Track Coupon Click (replace :id with actual coupon ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE/click

### ============================================
### SEARCH & TRENDING APIs (2)
### ============================================

### 15. Search Coupons
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?query=discount

### 16. Get Trending Coupons
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons/trending

### Get Trending with Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons/trending?limit=5

### ============================================
### TEST ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### API Status Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/test/status

### Test Dashboard
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test
